#

Pork Potato Delight

40 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodOne-Pan Meal

Description

A hearty and comforting dish featuring tender pork and creamy potatoes, all baked together for a deliciously simple meal.

Ingredients

  • pork chops: 4 pieces
  • potatoes: 4 medium
  • onion: 1 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • chicken broth: 1 cup
